---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 352
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
  - 987
  - 900
By: St Isaac the Syrian
---
When on one side we place all the actions of this life and on the
other silence, we find that it weighs down the scales. ... It is
better for you to cut yourself free from the bonds of sin than to
liberate slaves from their servitude.
